channel.title: Scanner Drivers
channel.description:
EDIT: After being down for a week, their FTP servers are back online. Got the driver. Fucking HP. :facepalm:
I need the drivers for an HP Scanjet 6300c.
The HP site "has them," but their FTP server is on the brink. The driver I'm looking for was released in 2009. I do not want anything older than that.
